  Locus:
    Page: 241
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Heart
---
Though a wealthy man with a large estate has many rooms in which to dwell,
he has one favorite sitting room in which he delights in being. The Lord
loves to dwell in the chamber of the heart of man.
